<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1362095" n="1"/>
<opener><abbr>Ill.<hi rend="sup">mo</hi></abbr> <choice><abbr>S.<hi rend="sup">re</hi></abbr><expan>Signore</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>S.<hi rend="sup">re</hi></abbr><expan>Signore</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>P<supplied>.</supplied>rone</abbr><expan>Patrone</expan></choice> Cel<supplied>.</supplied>mo
  <lb/><rs key="place_GEO-3167442" type="place">S. Angelo</rs> <date when="1719-08-01"><choice><abbr>p.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr><expan>primo</expan></choice> <abbr>Ag.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> 1719</date></opener>
  
  <note hand="pers_DE-588-119166895"><foreign xml:lang="ger"><abbr>Empf.</abbr> den <date when="1719-08-03">3.<hi rend="sup">ten</hi></date></foreign></note>
  
<p>Le <rs type="biblio">opere</rs> del <abbr>S.<hi rend="sup">r</hi></abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-104265264" type="person">Morgagni</rs> non uscirano in
                        <lb/><rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place"><abbr>Pad.<hi rend="sup">a</hi></abbr></rs> che alli <date>4</date>: <choice><orig><g ref="#per">&#42833;</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice>ò spero che avrò
                        <lb/>prima li due essemplari. VS$ faccia
                        <lb/>grazia <hi rend="u">mandare sabbato mattina in <rs type="place">campo
                        <lb/>alle beccarie</rs> e faccia dimandare <rs type="person">S<unclear>a</unclear>rgato</rs>
                        <lb/>gallinar da <rs key="GeoNamesID" type="place">S. Angelo</rs>, che <del/><add>da</add> esso</hi> (senza
                        <lb/>nessuna spesa) riceverà li due esemplari,
  <lb/>se mai li avrò potuti avere, e mi <choice><sic>favorià</sic><corr>favorirà</corr></choice>
                        <lb/>poi d'avvisarmene la ricevuta.</p>
<p>Hò consegnato il <unclear>v</unclear>igletto al <abbr>S.<hi rend="sup">r</hi></abbr> <rs type="person">Leandro</rs>, che
                        <lb/>le fà <choice><abbr>umil.<hi rend="sup">ma</hi></abbr><expan>umilissima</expan></choice> riverenza.</p>
<p>Mille grazie le rendo delle diligenze che farà
  <lb/>usare <choice><orig><g ref="#per">&#42833;</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice> quel Libro <hi rend="u"><rs type="biblio">Vitruvio</rs></hi><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118627252"/>, che assaissimo
                        <lb/>mi preme; così mille grazie <choice><orig><g ref="#per">&#42833;</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice> il <rs type="biblio"><abbr>Lib.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr></rs> speditomi,
                        <lb/>et infinite grazie <choice><orig><g ref="#per">&#42833;</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice> li benigni favori, che
  <lb/>Ella mi porta dell'<rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-102552517">ospite</rs> <add>suo</add>, cui fò
  <lb/><choice><abbr>umil.<hi rend="sup">ma</hi></abbr><expan>umilissima</expan></choice> riverenza; et auguro ogni felicità.</p>
<p>Io mene stò in questa villa, ove il caldo
                        <lb/>è meno grave, e si hà quiete, ne strepito di
                        <lb/>studio <choice><orig>Ancor</orig><reg>ancor</reg></choice> turbò questa r<add>i</add>mota parte.</p>
<p>Di vero cuore resto</p>
<closer>Di VS$
                        <lb/><choice><abbr>Div.<hi rend="sup">mo</hi></abbr><expan>Divotissimo</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Obbl.<hi rend="sup">mo</hi></abbr><expan>Obbligatissimo</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>ser.<hi rend="sup">e</hi></abbr><expan>servitore</expan></choice> et <choice><abbr>A.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr><expan>Amico</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>v.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr><expan>vero</expan></choice> <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-11887733X" type="person">Giovanni Poleni</rs></closer>
<pb facs="1362096" n="2" type="empty"/>
</div>
